## Summary: The Maintenance Calendar

```
EVERY COMMIT:
  - Linter passes
  - Type checker passes
  - Tests pass
  - No console.log or debug code

EVERY PR:
  - Reviewed against pattern checklist
  - No new tech debt without tracking issue
  - Documentation updated if behavior changed

WEEKLY (during normal work):
  - Clean up what you encounter (unused imports, old TODOs, commented code)

REGULARLY (at a cadence that fits your team):
  - Dependency vulnerability scan
  - Dead code scan
  - Test health check
  - Performance review

PERIODICALLY (less frequently - e.g. quarterly):
  - Major dependency updates
  - Architecture review
  - Documentation refresh
  - Security audit
```
